Create a Marketing Cloud Account Engagement Data Stream

Create a data stream and then configure the connector in Marketing Cloud Account Engagement to begin the flow of data.

Before you start, connect Account Engagement to Data Cloud. If you had set up this integration before the Spring ’24 release, update the connection by removing and adding your business units again.

In Data Cloud, go to the Data Streams tab and click New.
Select the Account Engagement data source, and click Next.
Select a business unit.
Select the type of data that you want to import.
Click Deploy.
In Marketing Cloud Account Engagement, configure the Data Cloud connector. See Importing Email Engagement Data from Account Engagement to Data Cloud to learn more.
